OL,3,CWellington cosmetics factory faces
OL,4,Cclosure with over 250 jobs under threat
OL,6,FMore than 250 workers at a Somerset
OL,7,Fcosmetics manufacturing plant are
OL,8,Ffacing an uncertain future after the
OL,9,Fcompany announced plans to shut down
OL,10,Fthe facility.
OL,12,FKDC/One, which operates the
OL,13,FSwallowfield site in Wellington and
OL,14,Franks among the town's major
OL,15,Femployers, has revealed proposals to
OL,16,Ftransfer operations to its Scottish
OL,17,Fbase in Irvine.
