OL,3,CWellington cosmetics factory faces
OL,4,Cclosure with over 250 jobs under threat
OL,6,FThe company described the decision as
OL,7,F"difficult" and confirmed it would
OL,8,Fbegin consulting with staff whilst
OL,9,Foffering the possibility of relocating
OL,10,Fto Scotland for those willing to make
OL,11,Fthe move.
OL,13,FThe announcement has drawn sharp
OL,14,Fcriticism from local MP Gideon Amos,
OL,15,Fwho expressed his shock at the timing
OL,16,Fof the proposal.
