OL,3,CWellington cosmetics factory faces
OL,4,Cclosure with over 250 jobs under threat
OL,6,FWriting to KDC/One chief executive
OL,7,FNicholas Whitley, Mr Amos highlighted
OL,8,Fthe factory's 149-year history in
OL,9,FWellington and questioned why the
OL,10,Fcompany had invested in upgrading the
OL,11,Fpremises during 2023-24 if closure was
OL,12,Fbeing contemplated.
OL,14,F"Your proposals are completely
OL,15,Funexpected given this context," the
OL,16,FTaunton and Wellington MP wrote,
OL,17,Fpressing the company to explore
OL,18,Fselling the operation as a functioning
OL,19,Fbusiness rather than simply shutting
OL,20,Fit down.
