OL,6,FMr Amos called on the firm to
OL,7,Fprioritise workers' interests and the
OL,8,Flocal community over "short-term
OL,9,Fconsiderations," suggesting the site
OL,10,Fremain operational whilst potential
OL,11,Fbuyers are sought.
OL,13,FIn response, KDC/One stated that
OL,14,Fsupporting employees through the
OL,15,F"proposed transition" remained their
OL,16,Fmain focus, though they did not
OL,17,Fdirectly address questions about
OL,18,Falternative options for the site's
OL,19,Ffuture.
